{"tid":1419217,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［連仔入］多個建議","createTime":"2019-08-06T00:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:35:06.000Z","uid":216800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f6e9cc5fcc313695e4b9e75b1e2fe0809b5aa9","tid":1419217,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:25:30.000Z","msg":"長期開PO/回覆大量負評 禁言30天<br />\n禁止及封鎖同一IP多帳號登入<br />\n設置帳號綁定裝置，禁止帳號在不同裝置登入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關於水軍洗正皮<br />\n我有一個構思：<br />\n凡正皮數多嘅post 連仔要係後台deta入邊檢視返有幾多個人成日幫特定人洗/互洗，正常黎講一人開po 一定係一班固定人會優先入去洗<br />\n但咁樣會大大增加工作量<br />\n所以要寫個code比系統自己判定，管理員只需作檢視<br />\n<br />\n如果會做禁言項措施，可以做多步<br />\n就係 在帳號名新增（1）<br />\n例如：連尼住(1) [P]<br />\n咁樣黎標示被禁言次數"},{"pid":"3723f132f07df37f3c8c1e01819bf68c0a67f2b7","tid":1419217,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2f90a74da2ff8071a921b72ab73a9f0f240e1b","tid":1419217,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a63b4940514ac5682fba48a0600cfceeae9f8a","tid":1419217,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9bca373f09a63af65ff2675ae68aa717de3b3c","tid":1419217,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}